      "options": {
        "content": "This dashboard is the operational bridge between metrics spikes, trace context, and raw logs. Use the `service`, `environment`, `level`, and optional `trace_id` filters to narrow logs first. For deep trace inspection, open Grafana Explore with the Tempo datasource and then pivot back into Loki using the provisioned trace-to-logs correlation. Direct trace search panels are intentionally deferred because the Explore workflow is more stable than embedding brittle Tempo-search panel JSON at this stage.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Use This Dashboard",
      "type": "text"
